description:
What it is: A skin-calming clay mask powered by tea-tree and squalane oil to help draw out impurities and balance oil while keeping skin ultra-soft.

Skin Type: Normal, Dry, Combination, and Oily

Skincare Concerns: Blemishes, Pores, and Redness

Formulation: Mask

Highlighted Ingredients:
- Tea Tree Oil: Purifies and calms skin.
- Squalane: Weightlessly locks in essential moisture.
- French Green Clay: Helps to draw impurities from congested skin.

Ingredient Callouts: This product is vegan, cruelty-free, and gluten-free.

What Else You Need to Know: Tea tree helps reduce the appearance of blemishes and other skin imperfections, while French green clay helps draw out impurities within pores. Antioxidant-rich matcha green tea helps keep skin calm. This non-drying formula features plant-derived squalane to leave skin feeling soft.

Clean at Sephora
When you spot our Clean seal, you can be sure we’ve checked that this brand’s product is made without the ingredients you told us you’d most like to avoid. 

Clean at Sephora™ is formulated without: 
Sulfates SLS and SLES, parabens, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, phthalates, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, triclosan, triclocarban. All skincare, hair, and makeup brands with the Clean Seal have less than one percent of synthetic fragrances.
name: Squalane + Tea Tree Detox Mask

description:
What it is: A quick-absorbing, weightless, and hydrating facial oil enhanced with tea tree oil and plant-derived squalane, a natural moisturizer.

Skin Type: Normal, Dry, Combination, and Oily

Skincare Concerns: Blemishes, Pores, and Redness

Formulation: Oil

Highlighted Ingredients:
- Tea Tree Oil: Purifies and calms skin.
- Squalane: Weightlessly locks in essential moisture.
- Rosemary Extract: Helps to prevent oxidation of oil on the skin.

Ingredient Callouts: This product is vegan, cruelty-free, and gluten-free.

What Else You Need to Know: Biossance’s exclusive tea tree and squalane combination helps reduce the appearance of blemishes, enlarged pores, and other imperfections. This oil is enriched with tea tree that originates from northern Australia, and is grown with the highest-quality eco-friendly, ISO-certified farming practices.

description:
Which skin type is it good for?
✔ Normal
✔ Oily
✔ Combination
✔ Dry
✔ Sensitive

What it is:
A multifunctional brightening formula.

Solutions for:
- Uneven skin tone
- Dullness and uneven texture
- Acne and blemishes

If you want to know more…
Azelaic Acid brightens the complexion while visibly improving the evenness of skin texture and reducing the look of blemishes. The multifunctional formula acts as an effective antioxidant and offers a very high 10 percent concentration of high-purity azelaic acid in a lightweight cream-gel format.

What it is formulated WITHOUT:
- Parabens
- Sulfates
- Phthalates

What else you need to know:
This product is vegan, cruelty-free, and formulated without alcohol, nuts, gluten, and fragrance.
name: Azelaic Acid Suspension 10%

description:

Each Lip Kit contains: 

  • 1 Matte Liquid Lipstick (0.11 oz./ 3.25 g)
  • 1 Pencil Lip Liner (net wt./ poids net  .03 oz/ 1.0g)

The #KylieCosmetics Lip Kit is your secret weapon to create the perfect 'Kylie Lip.' Each Lip Kit comes with a Matte Liquid Lipstick and matching Lip Liner.

Lip Liner
This ultra-long wearing lip liner has a creamy texture that glides across the lips for a very easy and comfortable application. The Lip Liner sharpens easily in most standard sized sharpeners - just make sure your sharpener is not dull!

Matte Liquid Lipstick
The Matte Liquid Lipstick has high intensity pigment for an instant bold matte lip. The extremely long wearing lipstick contains moisturizing ingredients for a comfortable, emollient and silky feel that does not dry your lips out.
